Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs22\c&H9BFFFF&}惊爆危机？校园篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(温柔常常是残酷的)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}优しさは时々　残酷だから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(越是追求越容易失去答案)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}求める程　こたえを见失う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(雨过天青的街道)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}雨上がりの街
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(如果能看见彩虹)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}虹が见えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(现在踏步向前吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}今　步きだそう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(会有什么好事发生的)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}何かが始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(因为有你因为还有明天)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}君がいるから　明日があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(因为一个人无法独自生活下去)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}一人きりじゃ生きてゆけないから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(觉得你那么靠近)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}こんなに近くに感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(这应该就是爱吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}それが爱でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(因为你了解泪水所代表的伤痛)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}泪の数の痛みを　君は知ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(在你清澈的双眼中)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}透き通るその目の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(寻找确切的意义)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}确かな意味を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&HD7DC07&}(想要找出笑容)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\fs20\c&H9BFFFF&}笑颜见つけたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是卓越安全科技公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前负责人不在座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在哔声後留话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝各位客户武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔，我是相良
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前拜托你的包裹已经送到了，可是内容物是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我订购的是枪的特殊瞄准具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是里面却只有一个奇怪的罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微看了一下说明书，里面装着非常危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗？居然空运这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上跟我联络
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打电话给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识的军火商
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要付钱，大部分的东西都可以帮你进货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明订了枪的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却搞错商品寄了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是个很坚固的水壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那么容易就会弄坏的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四班的相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关於施工中的社团大楼，我有点事情要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上到教职员办公室来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良，你又做了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有，我想不到有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看到施工现场拉了一条“禁止进入”的绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是好心，帮忙设了高压电陷阱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道为了这种事要怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要怪你\N(好痛…)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是施工的业者中了陷阱\N(好痛…)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以碰那个罐子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴虽然那么说\N其实还是很照顾他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是好暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买到了，买到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？小野D
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿街叫卖的“爆热神威咖哩面包”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都卖个精光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个新产品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说不是普通的辣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，我想先挑战看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要开动罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好夸张的反应\N好辣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野D，那是相良的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧，小野D
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个太辣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个面包店到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是宣传不就是这样说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家\N(一定会很辣的嘛)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看这个\N(对啊，你真是个冒失鬼)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好像很…很糟糕啊\N(明天要不要再挑战看看啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说…这一定很糟糕啊\N(真过份，我已经不敢吃超辣的了)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有没有听到啊\N(小野寺，你真是的)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听人家说话啊，你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn标楷体\c&H9BFFFF&}#17  第五堂课的危险区域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等要好好跟业者道歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见罗，恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人知道这个罐子里面的东西怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们老实说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓，我不会生气，也不会要求赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点自首
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它当成水壶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容物在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经打扫掉了，在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良，已经开始上课…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人听好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始禁止离开这间教室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也一样，不准离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是别班的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要踏进这间教室里的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是送了挑战书，叫你午休到屋顶上来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急状况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，这样不就出不去了吗\N(封锁严禁开放)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良，你也有点分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在…做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身装扮是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NBC(核生化)防护服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NB…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，首先要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良，你到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉，第五堂课必须紧急中止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间教室里，发生了非常重大的灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某国研究所试作的细菌武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从专用的容器中泄漏出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细…细菌武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由最先进的生物科技所创造出来，危险至极的细菌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生性贪婪凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经由空气感染人体之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃光猎物之前，绝对不会停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都记载在说明书上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个细菌，在这间教室里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都感染了吗？我也是？我的学生们也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾，恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点，她只是昏过去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能冷静下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感染？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急，不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们急得大吵大闹，事情也不会改善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少说这种自私的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感染以後就会死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你一个人穿着那么好的防护服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“不要急，不要慌”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有我对於细菌武器稍微有点了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找出有效的对策…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是只想让自已得救而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良，你居然敢那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子你们懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是因为爱惜自己的生命才这样指挥大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是以一个战斗专家的身分\N努力让状况不要恶化下去罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍去你们心中的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了接下来的事情着想，不要再去怨恨任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场悲剧不是任何人所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家懂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪和炸弹也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次居然是细菌武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙居然带了那么危险的东西进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪和炸弹也很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说是细菌武器根本就搞不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人觉得不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，先到保健室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想还是不要比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才相良说“不要离开这间教室”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为担心污染扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚他说过是经由空气传染的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们离开教室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个学校都会变成污染区了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是，没有人怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细菌武器的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是从感染到发病需要一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是杀伤力却十分惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至被称为“穷人的核子弹”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说中东某个国家正在研究伊波拉病毒的军事用途
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就是那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会全身喷血而死的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，别名“吃人病毒”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那个东西的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不可能会平安无事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家等一下，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没听到不可以离开教室吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做这种丢脸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会让受害范围扩大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的历史会如何记载这场灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们惊慌失措，把污染扩散到整个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人就会永远鄙视我们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟你们一样害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然会死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想在那之前尽情地吃“俄亥俄屋”的三叉戟烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有在车站前站着吃的面店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一碗加满所有能想到配料的超级豪华荞麦面以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再毫无遗憾地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心里是那么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你的死法还真便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算即将面临死亡，我们也要保持理性勇敢对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边祈祷着同胞们平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边将我们的身体献给「命运」这个活祭的祭坛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种高洁的精神光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是所谓的人性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟，你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是。不要再做这种丢脸的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很痛苦。不过，只要我们忍耐一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的以你们为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我说了那么多粗鲁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊，小要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家不是夥伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一个人死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在哭什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在体会人类的良心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就给我在那边死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打扰他们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有提到疫苗的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疫苗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细菌武器的疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了应付警急状况附在里面的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，只有一人份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是个把事情复杂化的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用抽签来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不用怨恨别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(抽到“中奖”的人可以获得疫苗)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都消失吧！大家都消失吧！大家都消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你告别…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点难过，不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天我都过得很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情…这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是谁？瑞树？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…\N瑞树？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不要在还没遇上好男人之前就死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是哪里搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求重来一次，而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做这种难看的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人，我不是不了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这种不乾脆的行为，只会玷污你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连这个都不懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是天命的话就接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是如何运用自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得真好，一成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来抽签吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心里没有悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，就算我抽中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一成，不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的爱一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜，下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫一成是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚被你骂了以後，我好心动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看起来也是个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都要死了，死前我们两个就结为夫妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘛，好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲姊，你打算怎么办呢\N(住…住手，不要抱我)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最後一个抽就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介呢？总之你也来抽一张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，抽中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中奖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，抽中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你抽中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里很不能接受…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的事情我都可以忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被细菌感染而死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会先因为这个宇宙的不合理抓狂而死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能够体会你们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我向你们保证
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会忘记这场悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把资料送给武器的开发者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且严厉地告诉他，避免再次发生这种惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静地接受你们的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，大家冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴力解决不了问题，我们坐下来谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要嘴里这样说还一边反击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要争执的那么难看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽签只要重来一次就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再让我伤心…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是班级秩序解体的小学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧不起教育也该有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是会空气传染的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤咲，你干的真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他什么污染区域！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉以前得去销毁偷拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从刚刚就想去上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细菌…细菌都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後都还是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么样的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我终於可以摆脱你惹出来的麻烦事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想想说不定还比较能够接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的这条命结束之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事无论如何都要结束掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向自己喜欢的女生告白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和家人告别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最後的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这女人别缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定在死前都要活在爱里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，我想说的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能跟你分出高下，我死也不暝目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧，我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现出你最後的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把所有的一切睹在这一击上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大导脉流最终奥义，临…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:16:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的连吐槽你的力气都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲姊，你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也知道事情的严重性了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想在心爱的人身边走完最後一程
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我无法达成这个心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样，我想一个人，品嚐一下最後的一杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去受你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我过来，马上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介，要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说没有时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管，跟我来就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室？为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，你在干什么啊，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟，把衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算马上就要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有作好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦，再怎么说实在也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也别说快点脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子就没什么好遗憾的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美树原？你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？为什么你会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是自习课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把习题全都做完了，就来这里处理剩下的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话，我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行，振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野D，振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个困难的要求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉身体已经动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界原来那么漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野D
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野D？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子，时候终於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我好像是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，小野D，你不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次看到你哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘，因为到最後了我才敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你…对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有股清爽的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀还有腰忽然变得很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，常盘！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了，相良。那不是什么杀人病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点说明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能分解石化制品的细菌\N从以前开始不是就很受瞩目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有研究人员想要作为军事用途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在实验过程中诞生了奇怪的细菌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那个细菌武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字就叫作“全裸病毒”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西在摄氏36度左右\N也就是只会在接近人体体温时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以惊人的速度繁殖、活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後它会产生将特定石化制品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说详细点就是把聚酯类以及尼龙给完全吃光的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个角度来说的话是一种非常凶猛的细菌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有疫苗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约两小时之後就会全部死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那段期间里不可以穿着石化制品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了天然纤维以外全都不行\N摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一旦发作之後\N是羊毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近的人通通都会受害\N学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你应该感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的副作用可以治疗肩膀僵硬以及腰部酸痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我再找你算帐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不是会致人於死的病毒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命，好像剩下不久了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是相良搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良搞的鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像跑走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤，怎么可以这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱还来，武本，贺东！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快写啊，志茂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,URUZU7呼叫本部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在遭到凶暴的当地人包围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽速安排脱离行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽速安排脱离行动\N找到了，在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他大卸八块


